you and I have been long-time traveling companions,

580
00:40:10,510 --> 00:40:12,670
你證明了自己是一個誠實勇敢
and you have proven yourself to be honest, brave,

581
00:40:12,670 --> 00:40:14,020
具備完全自我意識的人
and fully self-aware.

582
00:40:14,910 --> 00:40:16,780
我確信我欠你人情
I'm certain I owe you for things.

583
00:40:17,950 --> 00:40:19,330
你讓我幫你找解脫辦法
You asked me for a way out.

584
00:40:19,330 --> 00:40:20,800
我找到了一個
I had access to one.

585
00:40:23,850 --> 00:40:26,590
