590
00:41:54,080 --> 00:41:56,030
慢點  等等
Slow down. Come on. Whoa!

591
00:41:56,030 --> 00:41:57,860
他說他想幫我們
He says he wants to help us.

592
00:42:05,750 --> 00:42:06,840
是真的嗎
That true?

593
00:42:09,470 --> 00:42:10,860
你想幫忙
You want to help?

594
00:42:11,420 --> 00:42:12,620
是的
I do.

595
00:42:29,020 --> 00:42:30,210
好
Okay.

596
00:42:36,830 --> 00:42:38,530
跪下
Get on your knees.

